        {
            "title": "威高控股H股全流通獲中證監備案",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">威高控股(01066)宣佈，公司近期接獲中國證監會就實施H股全流通出具的備案通知書。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"威高股份官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/01066-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"威高股份官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/01066-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">威高股份官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據備案通知書，公司已就4830萬股未上市股份（相當於本公佈日期本公司已發行股本總額約1.06%）轉換為H股完成在中國證監會的備案。於完成有關轉換及聯交所授予批准上市後，股份將於聯交所主板上市買賣。備案通知書自2027年3月26日起計有效期為12個月。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15826661-%e5%a8%81%e9%ab%98%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1h%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%b5%81%e9%80%9a%e7%8d%b2%e4%b8%ad%e8%ad%89%e7%9b%a3%e5%82%99%e6%a1%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/01066-Web2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:58:18",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "腦動極光成為北京前沿腦機接口研究院戰略合作單位",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">腦動極光(06681)公布，於近期正式成為北京前沿腦機接口研究院的戰略合作單位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"腦動極光官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/BrainAurora.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"腦動極光官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/BrainAurora.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">腦動極光官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司之子公司浙江腦動極光醫療科技於3月27日，與北京前沿腦機接口研究院現場簽署戰略合作協議。<br/> <br/>   北京前沿腦機接口研究院於2026年3月由首都醫科大學宣武醫院牽頭成立。研究院聚焦腦機接口領域核心技術攻堅與臨床轉化，研究院將建成覆蓋神經電生理數據資源、智能算法開發、器械開發測試、前臨床驗證、生物樣本庫、臨床驗證與第三方評價的六大共性支撐平台。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15826626-%e8%85%a6%e5%8b%95%e6%a5%b5%e5%85%89%e6%88%90%e7%82%ba%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e5%89%8d%e6%b2%bf%e8%85%a6%e6%a9%9f%e6%8e%a5%e5%8f%a3%e7%a0%94%e7%a9%b6%e9%99%a2%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c%e5%96%ae",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/06681.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:52:01",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "京東發行100億人幣票據",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">京東(09618)公布，發行本金總額為100億元人民幣的優先無擔保票據，票據將於聯交所上市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100億票據包括2031年到期的75億元人民幣2.05厘票據及2036年到期的25億元人民幣2.75厘票據，募集資金淨額用於一般公司用途，包括償還若干現有債務及支付利息。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">京東預期，於2026年4月10日或前後完成票據發行，受滿足慣例完成條件所規限。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15826620-%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1%e7%99%bc%e8%a1%8c100%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e7%a5%a8%e6%93%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260302_FI_source-web_09618-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:38:14",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期升58點  ADR高水43點  石藥跑贏",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期升58點或0.23%，報25318。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR較恆指昨日收市高43點或0.17%，報25337點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">石藥(01093)ADR折合港元計收報9.99元，較香港收市價升3.90%，跑贏其他藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報133.97元，較香港收市價升2.8%，貢獻恒指55點 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣121.23元，較香港收市價低1.2%，影響恒指22點，兩股為影響恒指主要動力。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR折合港元計收報497.73元，較香港收市價0.2% ; 美團(03690)ADR折合港元計收報81.71元，較香港收市價跌0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">友邦保險(01299)ADR收市折合港幣87.75元，較香港收市價高0.3% ; 港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣401.56元，較香港收市價0.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">理想汽車(02105)ADR收市折合港幣72.05元，較香港收市價高1.2% ; 比亞迪(01211)ADR收市折合港幣104.41元，較香港收市價低0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報25301點，升3點，較昨日恒指收市25294點，高水7點，成交20653張。國指夜市期指收報8491點，較昨日國指收市低水14點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15826617-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%8d%8758%e9%bb%9e-adr%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b443%e9%bb%9e-%e7%9f%b3%e8%97%a5%e8%b7%91%e8%b4%8f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:33:17",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "紐油曾見96.5美元  布油收跌2.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價下跌，美伊戰爭或結束，此外美國石油庫存增幅高於預期。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油5月合約一度回落4.81%，低見每桶96.5美元，收報100.12美元，跌1.2% ; 倫敦布蘭特期油6月合約收報每桶101.16美元，跌2.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國總統特朗普表示美國快將結束對伊朗的戰爭，消息影響油價。此外，美國能源信息署(EIA)數據顯示，美國上星期原油庫存大幅增加550萬桶，增幅遠高於預期，庫存增至近3年高位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15826441-%e7%b4%90%e6%b2%b9%e6%9b%be%e8%a6%8b96-5%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83-%e5%b8%83%e6%b2%b9%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c2-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/8a6d6fb35c89d9b0db4c4846f290c2c3_Iran_US_Oil_Prices_19824_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:18:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大圍柏傲莊升逾23%1100萬承接  買家追價20萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15816249&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中原地產沙田豪宅市中心分行表示，大圍柏傲莊3月暫錄約12宗二手成交，屋苑最新錄2期6B座中層F室，單位實用面積464平方呎，2房間隔，叫價約1080萬元，其後反價20萬元，以1100萬元獲承接，實用面積平均呎價23707元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據了解，新買家為區內用家，原業主於2020年以約893萬元購入單位，持貨約6年，是次易手賬面獲利207萬元離場，單位期內升值23.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15816249-%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%8d%e6%9f%8f%e5%82%b2%e8%8e%8a%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be23%1100%e8%90%ac%e6%89%bf%e6%8e%a5-%e8%b2%b7%e5%ae%b6%e8%bf%bd%e5%83%b920%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260302_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:07:07",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "差估署 : 2月樓價按年升7.7% 按月升近1.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15798577&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">差餉物業估價署數據顯示，2月全港私人住宅樓價指數升至307.6，按月升1.59%，按年升7.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中小型單位(100方米以下)售價指數按月升1.61%；較大面積單位(100平方米或以上)售價指數按月升1.39%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">當中，A類物業(40平方米以下)售價指數按月升1.62%；B類物業(40至69.9平方米)按月升1.69%；C類物業(70至99.9平方米)按月升1.21%；D類物業(100至159.9平方米)按月升1.53%；E類物業(160平方米或以上)按月升0.92%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">租金指數方面，2月私人住宅租金指數升至200.8，按月升0.05%，按年升4.04%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今年首兩月，私人住宅樓價指數升2.64%；租金指數升0.15%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15798577-%e5%b7%ae%e4%bc%b0%e7%bd%b2-2%e6%9c%88%e6%a8%93%e5%83%b9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%877-7-%e6%8c%89%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%911-6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240726_PP_PROPERTY_INDEX_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 08:07:07",
